{"tid":633360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞漢元州邨偷奶粉　途人合力追50米按地制服","createTime":"2018-04-18T08:45:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T07:30:06.000Z","uid":75969,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"1a335918cb9013ad6fa4eaacd9357d702f3023cb","tid":633360,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T08:45:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180418/photo/bkn-20180418123020542-0418_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180418141231\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180418%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180418123020542-0418_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180418141231&h=d4d52b73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">涉案南亞漢被捕。(曾志恒攝)</span><br />\n<br />\n深水埗元州邨地下一間個人護理連鎖店，早上11時38分，一名20餘歲南亞漢在店內偷走兩罐奶粉後離開，惟觸動門口的防盜警號，立即拔足逃走。女職員發現追出呼叫，驚動數名熱心途人合力追截，終在50米外近元泰樓對開，將男子截停並且按在地上制服，期間，南亞漢曾將其中一罐奶粉棄掉地上，警方接報到場調查，將其拘捕帶署。據悉，被捕南亞漢持行街紙留港。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180418/photo/bkn-20180418123020542-0418_00822_001_06b.jpg?20180418141231\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180418%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180418123020542-0418_00822_001_06b.jpg%3F20180418141231&h=092949a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180418/bkn-20180418123020542-0418_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180418%2Fbkn-20180418123020542-0418_00822_001.html&d=tqRGKOaiWHhoCo5CzJ7%2Bzr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=358d534f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180418/bkn-20180418123020542-0418_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3e9e421be668cbc84a3e58842e2a3f177eb62d7f","tid":633360,"uid":75969,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T08:46:24.000Z","msg":"南亞仔又加一分<br />\n休班警爭氣少少啦 比人扒頭喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eecaa8da5fd128b71a2199b946